high_descs: Walk out of the office, straight through the hall, into the bedroom, around to the other side of the bed, and over to the wood dresser in the corner.
Pick up the spatula that is on the wood dresser in the corner, next to the bed.
Walk around the bowl, out of the bedroom, make a right into the hall, walk into the living room, past the couch, and over to the TV stand below the TV on the wall.
Put the spatula into the bowl on the TV stand.
Pick up the bowl with the spatula in it from the TV stand.
Walk slightly to the right of the diningtable.
Place the bowl with the spatula in it onto the lower shelf of the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Put a spatula into the bowl to store in the diningtable.

high_descs: Go straight turn right to reach the dresser.
Pick the spatula from the table.
Turn right to exit the room and go straight to reach the bowl on the table.
Put the spatula into the bowl kept on the table.
Collect the bowl along with the spoon.
Turn right and head to the diningtable.
Again place the bowl along with the spoon on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Place the spatula along with the bowl on the diningtable.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the bedroom in the opposite, then go to the dresser to your right, next to the bed.
Pick up the spatula on the side table.
Turn around and go along left to the bed, then go through the right side doorway, hang a right, walk past the sofa, then turn right, and go to the bowl table to your left.
Put the spatula in the bowl on the left side of the table.
Pick up the bowl with the flat turner in it.
Turn right and move to the center of the diningtable.
Put the bowl on the right side of the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl along with a flat turner on the diningtable
